title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show SEP-05-2014 FRI
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show SEP-05-2014 FRI



Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20140905  03 Open Lines

Prager H3: Per usual callers set the agenda. 
  Issues raised include: 

  is it possible to be successful when marrying individuals 
     with different values; 

  can a Jew or non-Christian benefit from reading the New Testament;

  would an eleven year gap in a relationship work; 

  how do you explain to children why the Jews and Israel are hated so much?




Prager 20140905  02 Happiness Hour: Being An Easy Parent

Prager H2: Should you be a hard or easy parent once
        the child is a young adult?




Prager 20140905  01 The Real Rape Culture Pt. 2

Prager H1: Dennis opens the show with more about the girls 
     in Rotherham being raped and tortured by Pakistani men.
        The police in the city have done nothing because they are afraid
           of being called racist. 

    Dennis wonders where the outrage from feminists is over the 
         real rape culture. 

     Attempted forced kissing is now considered sexual assault.
